Comments: SEVERAL LARGE DIAMETER HARDWOOD TREES WERE SNAPPED NEAR THE TRUNK OF THE TREES AT A SEASONAL CAMP NEAR LAKE SUPERIOR. THE MAST FOR THE ELECTRICAL SERVICE WAS BENT OFF. (MQT)
3 LARGE TREES UPROOTED. EACH WERE ABOUT 2 FT IN DIAMETER. YARD FURNITURE WAS ALSO BLOWN ABOUT 50 FT AND 70 LB GRILL WAS BLOWN OVER. TIME ESTIMATED VIA RADAR. (MQT)
